{{TagLine|AX11000 Tri Band 802.11ax WiFi Router}} :{{ProductPage|https://www.asus.com/Networking/RT-AX95U/}} {{SupportPage|vendor=ASUS|model=RT-AX95U}} *''Wireless-AX11000 Tri-band Gigabit Router'' :Supporting MU-MIMO and OFDMA technology, :built-in WTFast game accelerator and Adaptive QoS, :with AiProtection network security powered by Trend Micro *Web GUI: http://router.asus.com {{see also|ASUS GT-AX11000|ASUS RT-AX88U|ASUS RT-AX92U}} According to FCC documents, the [[ASUS RT-AX95U|RT-AX95U]] and the [[ASUS GT-AX11000|GT-AX11000]] :(renamed from RT-AX11000) are identical. ===Overview=== *'''Next-Gen WiFi Standard''' - 802.11ax WiFi standard for better efficiency and throughput *'''Ultrafast WiFi Speed''' - 11Gbps WiFi speed to handle even the busiest network with ease *'''Wider Usage and More Convenience''' - 8 antennas + 8 LAN ports to support more clients *'''Commercial-grade Security''' - AiProtection, powered by Trend Micro, blocks internet :security threats for all your connected smart devices *'''Better Partner with Mesh System''' - Compatible with ASUS AiMesh WiFi system :for seamless whole-home coverage ===News=== *[https://www.asus.com/us/News/rU7DdBAsBXMQ5cn0 ''ASUS Announces a Complete Lineup of 802.11ax Routers'' on '''ASUS'''] *[https://edgeup.asus.com/2018/asus-introduces-family-802-11ax-routers-for-busy-wifi-networks/ ''ASUS Introduces a Complete Family of 802.11ax Routers'' on '''ASUS'''] ===Forum threads=== *[https://www.snbforums.com/threads/and-so-it-begins-asus-announces-first-802-11ax-router.41020/page-4#post-382840 ''And So It Begins... Asus Announces First 802.11ax Router'' on '''SNB''' forums] *[https://www.snbforums.com/threads/asus-expands-11ax-lineup-and-sets-ship-date.47010/ ''ASUS Expands 11ax Lineup And Sets Ship Date'' on '''SNB''' forums]
